reviewText: It was a gift, my kid loved it and found it interesting.
Gave as gift. DVD was interesting.
Great gift for that gift that no one else will be giving.  Very fun for the receiver!

Husband bought for my birthday.  Loved this "memory lane" gift! It was awesome.  To go with this he also downloaded a song from the top 40 for each year since 1974 for me.  What a treat, brought back so many memories, these gifts!
